#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-27B-Qwen3.6-27B.md:1
msgid "Qwen3.5-27B/Qwen3.6-27B"
msgstr "Qwen3.5-27B/Qwen3.6-27B"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-27B-Qwen3.6-27B.md:3
msgid "1 Introduction"
msgstr "1 简介"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-27B-Qwen3.6-27B.md:5
msgid ""
"Qwen3.5-27B and Qwen3.6-27B are dense hybrid Mamba-Transformer language "
"models in the Qwen3.5/Qwen3.6 family, integrating breakthroughs in "
"architectural efficiency, reinforcement learning scale, and global "
"accessibility. They share the same hybrid attention design (GDN + full "
"attention), so deployment on Ascend NPUs follows the same pattern for "
"both models. They are suitable for general-purpose text generation tasks "
"such as dialogue, content creation, and code generation running on Ascend"
" NPUs."
msgstr ""
"Qwen3.5-27B和Qwen3.6-27B是Qwen3.5/Qwen3.6系列中的密集混合Mamba-Transformer语言模型，集成了架构效率、强化学习规模和全球可访问性方面的突破。它们共享相同的混合注意力设计（GDN + 全注意力），因此在Ascend NPU上的部署对两个模型遵循相同的模式。它们适用于在Ascend NPU上运行的通用文本生成任务，如对话、内容创作和代码生成。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-27B-Qwen3.6-27B.md:7
msgid ""
"This document will demonstrate the main validation steps for the models, "
"including supported features, feature configuration, environment "
"preparation, single-node and multi-node deployment, as well as accuracy "
"and performance evaluation."
msgstr ""
"本文档将演示模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的功能、功能配置、环境准备、单节点和多节点部署，以及准确性和性能评估。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-27B-Qwen3.6-27B.md:9
msgid ""
"It is **strongly recommended to use the latest release candidate (rc) "
"version or the latest official version** of `vllm-ascend`. As a minimum-"
"version requirement, `Qwen3.5-27B` is first supported in `vllm-"
"ascend:v0.17.0rc1`, and `Qwen3.6-27B` is first supported in `vllm-"
"ascend:v0.18.0rc1`."
msgstr ""
"**强烈建议使用`vllm-ascend`的最新候选发布（rc）版本或最新正式版本**。作为最低版本要求，`Qwen3.5-27B`首次支持于`vllm-ascend:v0.17.0rc1`，`Qwen3.6-27B`首次支持于`vllm-ascend:v0.18.0rc1`。"

